00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,035
Another interesting study is on the certificates issued by certificate authorities.

2
00:00:06,035 --> 00:00:10,440
This is an important topic because HTTPS underlines

3
00:00:10,440 --> 00:00:14,087
all secure Web communications and HTTPS

4
00:00:14,087 --> 00:00:18,355
is depending on the security of certificate authorities.

5
00:00:18,355 --> 00:00:19,740
The problem is that there are

6
00:00:19,740 --> 00:00:24,875
many certificate authorities and every one of them can sign for any website.

7
00:00:24,875 --> 00:00:29,110
In fact, we don't even know all the certificate authorities, until we see them.

